Day 15 — DOM Manipulation

Interview Questions:

How does DOM work?
:- The Document object modal(DOM) is programming interface for web document. it represect html or xml page as object tree. each node is refet to atribute,element and text. this structure allow javacript to dynamically access, modify and interact with content, structure  and style.

On load it's create dom, enabled script to update the page without reloading. for example you change the text, add element and change the color.


